{"word":"H816 - אָשַׁם - ʼâsham - aw-sham' - [idiom] certainly","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָשַׁם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâsham"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-sham'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] certainly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"குற்றவாளியாயிரு குற்றஞ் செய், பாழாக்கு, சேதப்படுத்து, குற்றஞ் சுமத்து, குற்றவாளியாக்கு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to offend, to be guilty, to trespass"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to do wrong, to offend, to trespass, to commit an"},{"paragraph":"offense, to do injury"},{"paragraph":"2)to be or to become guilty"},{"paragraph":"3) to be held guilty"},{"paragraph":"4) to be incriminated"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to suffer punishment"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to declare guilty"},{"paragraph":"2) to be desolate, to acknowledge offense"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; <i>to be guilty</i>; by implication to <i>be punished</i> or <i>perish: - </i> X certainly, be (-come, made) desolate, destroy, X greatly, be (-come, found, hold) guilty, offend (acknowledge offence), trespassive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H816 - אָשַׁם - ʼâsham - aw-sham'/816\">H816</a>, <a href=\"#/H817 - אָשָׁם - ʼâshâm - aw-shawm'/817\">H817</a>, <a href=\"#/H818 - אָשֵׁם - ʼâshêm - aw-shame'/818\">H818</a>, <a href=\"#/H819 - אַשְׁמָה - ʼashmâh - ash-maw'/819\">H819</a>"}]}